title: Billiards/Game Room,  TV/Theatre Room, Social Lounge!
posting_body: ['Designed for modern luxury living, the newly renovated apartment homes at The Meadows offer the lifestyle you desire.', 'Our pet-friendly one and two bedroom apartments in Tacoma, Washington, feature open-concept floor plans with spacious living areas.', 'Sleek stainless-steel appliances, handsome custom cabinetry, and warm wood-style plank flooring are a few of the finishes that add elegance to your space.', 'Each home includes a covered balcony or patio where you can kick back and relax in the fresh air with your pup.', 'Resort-style amenities await at The Meadows.', 'Treat yourself to a refreshing swimming pool, 24-hour fitness center, and a stylish clubhouse with fireplace lounge and complimentary WiFi.', 'Exceptional living begins here.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Dog Park', 'Gated Electronic Entrance', 'Window Coverings', 'Onsite Management', 'Built-In Linen Storage Closets', 'Pre-Wired for Cable Television', 'Walk-In Closet', 'Clubhouse', 'Spacious Floorplans', 'Media Center', 'Assigned Covered Parking', 'TV / Theatre Room', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
